@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1 id="saascade-components">SAAScade Components</h1>

<div class="doc-layout">

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="welcome">Welcome</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Get started with Saascade, one of the world's most popular Blazor component
            frameworks for building feature rich, blazing fast applications.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <p>
            Saascade consists of modern UI components with customizable styling,
            comprehensive documentation, UI design assets, and the tooling you need
            to build a solid foundation for your applications.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Quickly get a project started with any of our examples.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <p>
            The <a href="/quick-start">quick start</a> guide will take you through
            downloading and getting started with Saascade.
        </p>

        <p>
            The best way to round up the whole story is to see Saascade in action.
        </p>

        <h3>Installation</h3>
        <pre><code>dotnet add package Saascade.Blazor.Components</code></pre>

        <h3>Register a Design System</h3>
        <pre><code>builder.Services.AddSingleton&lt;IDesignSystem&gt;(DesignSystems.Tailwind.DaisyUI);</code></pre>

        <h3>Add Imports</h3>
        <pre><code>@@using Saascade.Blazor.Components</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="design-systems">Design Systems</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Saascade components are design-system-agnostic — swap CSS frameworks without changing your markup.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <ul>
            <li><a href="/bootstrap5">Bootstrap 5</a> — vanilla Bootstrap classes.</li>
            <li><a href="/daisyui">Tailwind / DaisyUI</a> — Tailwind with DaisyUI plugin.</li>
            <li><a href="/basecoat">Tailwind / Basecoat</a> — Tailwind with Basecoat plugin.</li>
            <li><a href="/custom-themes">Custom Themes</a> — create your own design system.</li>
        </ul>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="ai-integration">AI Integration</h2>

        <p>
            Use an AI assistant? Connect it to the
            <a href="/mcp-server-guide">MCP server</a>
            to pull Saascade docs and examples on demand.
        </p>

    </section>

</main>

